== 反响 ==
《橡皮头》上映后，《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》对其评价不佳，称电影“令人作呕”、“品味低劣”<ref name="variety" />。评论中对这部电影经过长时间的酝酿表示难以置信，还形容其结局令人无法观看<ref name="variety">{{cite web | url = http://variety.com/1976/film/reviews/eraserhead-1200424018/ | title = Variety Reviews – Eraserhead – Film Reviews – – Review by Variety Staff | publisher = ''Variety'' | year = 1977 | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504110710/http://variety.com/1976/film/reviews/eraserhead-1200424018/ | archivedate = 2014-05-04}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的汤姆·巴克利（{{lang|en|Tom Buckley}}）将本片与林奇的下一部作品《[[象人_(电影)|象人]]》（{{lang|en|''The Elephant Man''}}）对比，认为后者制作精良、演员表演出色，但《橡皮头》没能做到这两点。巴克利称本片“昏昏沉沉、自命不凡”，觉得电影的恐怖仅仅源于畸形儿的形象，而非剧本和演出<ref name="nyt1980">{{cite news | title = The Screen: 'Eraserhead' | first = Buckley | last = Tom | newspaper = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 1980-10-17 | page = C15}}</ref>。《[[大西洋_(杂志)|大西洋]]》（{{lang|en|''The Atlantic''}}）的劳埃德·罗斯（{{lang|en|Lloyd Rose}}）在1984年撰文称，《橡皮头》证明林奇是“电影行业最纯粹的超现实主义者之一”<ref name="atlantic">{{cite web | via = HighBeam Research | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-211473134.html | title = Tumoresque: the films of David Lynch | first = Lloyd | last = Rose | work = The Atlantic | publisher = Atlantic Media Company | date = 1984-10-01 | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130513005719/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-211473134.html | archive-date = 2013-05-13 | dead-url = yes }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。罗斯认为电影有着强烈的个性，与之前的超现实主义电影，如[[路易斯·布努埃尔|路易斯·布努埃尔]]1929年的《[[一条安达鲁狗|一条安达鲁狗]]》或1930年的《[[黄金时代_(1930年电影)|黄金时代]]》（{{lang|fr|''L'Age d'Or''}}）都不一样，林奇的想象“不会通过他的电影主动接触我们，（而是）我们沉入到它们（他的电影和想象）中去”<ref name="atlantic" />。迈克尔·威尔明顿（{{lang|en|Michael Wilmington}}）于1983年在《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》上称本片是一部独一无二的电影，觉得这部电影的“强度”和“噩梦清晰度”都是林奇在创作过程中关注细节的结果，尤其是他在影片制作过程中还同时身兼那么多不同岗位工作的情况下<ref name="tribune">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-05-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504072556/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1993-11-19/entertainment/9311190246_1_jack-nance-henry-spencer-star | title = Eraserhead Makes Its Mark As A Monument To Alienation | first = Michael | last = Wilmington | url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1993-11-19/entertainment/9311190246_1_jack-nance-henry-spencer-star | date = 1993-11-19 | work = Chicago Tribune | publisher = Tribune Company | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。影评人乔纳森·罗森鲍姆（{{lang|en|Jonathan Rosenbaum}}）在1995年的文章《坏主意：双峰的艺术和政治》（{{lang|en|''Bad Ideas: The Art and Politics of Twin Peaks''}}）中称，《橡皮头》代表着林奇最优秀的作品。他觉得这位导演的艺术天份随着知名度的增加而有所下降，并援引当时林奇最新的作品《[[我心狂野|我心狂野]]》（{{lang|en|''Wild at Heart''}}，[[1990年电影|1990年]]）作为这种天份下降的明证，称“即使是对《橡皮头》和《我心狂野》进行最粗略的对比也会发现，艺术（品质）的下跌是如此之快，以致于实在难以想象两部影片是出于同一人之手”<ref name="Rosenbaum-1995">{{cite book | title = Full of Secrets: Critical Approaches to Twin Peaks | last1 = Rosenbaum | first1 = Jonathon | editor1-first = David | editor1-last = Lavery | year = 1995 | publisher = Wayne State University Press | isbn = 0-8143-2506-8 | chapter = Bad Ideas: The Art and Politics of Twin Peaks | edition = illustrated | page = 23}}</ref>。

21世纪后，电影获得了普遍的好评。根据[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上收集的45篇评论文章，其中有41篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为91%，[[加权平均数|平均得分]]8.2（最高10分），网站上的评论共识这样写道：“大卫·林奇的超现实主义电影《橡皮头》通过使用细致的视觉效果和令人毛骨悚然的音乐，对一个男人为人父母的恐惧进行了怪异而令人不安的描绘”<ref name="rotten">{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eraserhead/ | title = Eraserhead (1977) | work = Rotten Tomatoes | publisher = Flixster | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archive-date = 2021-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227012130/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eraserhead | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[帝国杂志|帝国]]》杂志的史蒂夫·比尔德（{{lang|en|Steve Beard}}）给予本片五星的高度评价（最高五星），认为影片“远比（林奇）之后在好莱坞的作品更激进，更让人享受”，并特别称赞了其中将超现实主义[[肉体恐怖|肉体恐怖]]和[[黑色幽默|黑色喜剧]]相结合的处理方式<ref name="empire">{{cite web | url = http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=14647 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521152740/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=14647 | title = Empire's Eraserhead Movie Review | first = Steve | last = Beard | work = Empire | publisher = Bauer Media Group | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2013-05-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的奥尔马尔·哈弗里达森（{{lang|en|Almar Haflidason}}）对电影的评价为三星（最高五星），认为与林奇之后的标准相比，本片算是一次“不起眼的壮举”<ref name="bbc">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090224010552/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/01/16/eraserhead_1977_review.shtml | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/01/16/eraserhead_1977_review.shtml | title = BBC – Films – review – Eraserhead | first = Almar | last = Haflidason | date = 2001-01-16 | publisher = BBC | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2009-02-24}}</ref>。哈弗里达森认为，影片把一堆略有关联的理念集结在一起，「采用了如此之多的超现实主义意像，因而拥有着无限可能，让每个人都可以把自己的理论套用其中」，他对本片的主题理解是，电影代表了对个人承诺的恐惧，并且“性欲在其中暗流涌动”<ref name="bbc" />。{{lang|en|[[Film4|Film4]]}}的一篇评论给予《橡皮头》五星评价（最高五星），形容影片“时而优美、时而讨厌、时而风趣、时而可气……但始终带有让人紧张的能量”<ref name="film4">{{cite web | url = http://www.film4.com/reviews/1977/eraserhead | title = Eraserhead (1977) – Film Review | work = Film4 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504071352/http://www.film4.com/reviews/1977/eraserhead | publisher = Channel Four Television Corporation | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-05-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。这篇评论中还认为，《橡皮头》和当时已经上映的大部分电影都截然不同，只与路易斯·布努埃尔和[[萨尔瓦多·达利|萨尔瓦多·达利]]合作的作品类似；不过，林奇表示自己在制作本片前没有看过这两位电影人的任何作品<ref name="film4" />。《[[乡村之声|乡村之声]]》（{{lang|en|''The Village Voice''}}）的内森·李称赞了片中采用的音效，称“（单）看这部电影没有任何意义——（你）必须还得听”<ref name="village">{{cite web|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2007-01-09/film/david-lynch-made-a-man-out-of-me/ |title=David Lynch Made a Man Out of Me |work=The Village Voice |publisher=Village Voice Media |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103143019/http://www.villagevoice.com/2007-01-09/film/david-lynch-made-a-man-out-of-me/ |first=Nathan |last=Lee |date=2007-01-09 |accessdate=2014-09-05 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。他形容电影的音效听起来就像一个身材高大的人在吃了[[D-麦角酸二乙胺|迷幻药]]后把一个星系的贝壳都堆到耳边来听<ref name="village" />。

《卫报》的彼得·布拉德肖（{{lang|en|Peter Bradshaw}}）同样赞赏了这部电影，给予五星的高度评价（最高五星）。布拉德肖认为这是一部美丽的影片，形容其音效设计如同“工业性的呻吟，仿佛电影是在某个倒塌的工厂或是巨大的垂死生物中拍摄一般”<ref name="guardian">{{cite web | date = 2008-09-12 | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504110035/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/sep/12/horror1?INTCMP=SRCH | url = http://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/sep/12/horror1?INTCMP=SRCH | title = Film review: Eraserhead {{!}} Film | publisher = Guardian News and Media | first = Peter | last = Bradshaw | archivedate = 2014-05-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。他还着重指出了电影的肉体恐怖元素，将其与[[雷德利·斯科特|雷德利·斯科特]][[1979年电影|1979年]]的《[[异形_(电影)|异形]]》对比<ref name="guardian" />。{{lang|en|[[All_Media_Guide|All Media Guide]]}}的基思·菲普斯（{{lang|en|Keith Phipps}}）给予本片四星评分（最高五星），他也强调了影片令人不安的音效设计，称其是“一个开放式的隐喻”<ref name="rovi" />。他还感觉，《橡皮头》中导演表现出来的种种痴迷将会伴随他的整个职业生涯，他也相信，这种电影的超现实主义风格有助于增强对导演之后作品的理解<ref name="rovi" />。导演[[马克·埃文斯|马克·埃文斯]]（{{lang|en|Marc Evans}}）在《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》上撰文称赞了本片的音效设计和林奇“让普通看起来如此古怪”的能力，觉得这部电影是自己执导影片的灵感来源<ref name="telegraph">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140602024209/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3583763/Film-makers-on-film-Marc-Evans.html | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3583763/Film-makers-on-film-Marc-Evans.html | title = Film makers on film: Marc Evans | first1 = Marc | last1 = Evans | first2 = Mark | last2 = Monahan | publisher = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2002-10-05 | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-06-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。该报还刊登了另一篇评论，将《橡皮头》与[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]][[剧作家|剧作家]][[萨缪尔·贝克特|萨缪尔·贝克特]]的作品相比，形容影片是对家庭生活的一次混乱模仿<ref name="telegraph2">{{cite web | title = DVD reviews: Charley Varrick, Iron Man, Eraserhead, The Short Films of David Lynch, Festen 10th Anniversary Edition | first = David | last = Cheal | work = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2008-10-22 | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-06-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140602024206/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/3562417/DVD-reviews-Charley-Varrick-Iron-Man-Eraserhead-The-Short-Films-of-David-Lynch-Festen-10th-Anniversary-Edition.html | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/3562417/DVD-reviews-Charley-Varrick-Iron-Man-Eraserhead-The-Short-Films-of-David-Lynch-Festen-10th-Anniversary-Edition.html}}</ref>。《纽约时报》的马诺拉·达吉斯（{{lang|en|Manohla Dargis}}）认为影片更像是超现实主义的集合，而不是一个简单的故事<ref name="nyt rev" />，他还觉得影片的画面让人想到[[弗兰西斯·培根_(画家)|弗兰西斯·培根]]的画作和[[乔治·弗朗叙|乔治·弗朗叙]]（{{lang|en|Georges Franju}}）1949年的[[纪录片|纪录片]]《[[野兽之血|野兽之血]]》（{{lang|en|''Blood of the Beasts''}}）<ref name="nyt rev" />。{{lang|en|[[Film_Threat|Film Threat]]}}网站的菲尔·霍尔（{{lang|en|Phil Hall}}）称《橡皮头》是林奇最优秀的电影，认为这位导演之后的作品都没有达到本片的高度<ref name="threat">{{cite web | url = http://www.filmthreat.com/reviews/8630/ | title = Film Threat – Eraserhead (DVD) | first = Phil | last = Hall | publisher = ''Film Threat'' | date = 2006-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504072611/http://www.filmthreat.com/reviews/8630/ | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-04}}</ref>。霍尔特别指出，电影的声音方面表现，以及南斯那种“[[查理·卓别林|卓别林式]]”的形体喜剧演出，都是电影中表现突出的元素<ref name="threat" />。

== 影响 ==
2004年，《橡皮头》因其在“文化、历史和审美方面的显著成就”，由[[国会图书馆_(美国)|美国国会图书馆]]列入[[国家电影登记部|国家电影登记部]]下属的[[国家电影登记表|国家电影登记表]]保护电影名单<ref name="2004Add">{{cite press release | title = Films Added to National Film Registry for 2004 | publisher = Library of Congress | date = 2004-12-28 | archivedate = 2014-08-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814211628/http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2004/04-215.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2004/04-215.html | accessdate = 2014-09-05}}</ref>。影片是[[2005年电影|2005年]]纪录片《午夜电影史》（{{lang|en|''Midnight Movies: From the Margin to the Mainstream''}}）的主题之一，其中讲述了20世纪60年代末到70年代午夜场电影的兴起，林奇为此接受了一系列的采访。纪录片中把午夜场电影的出现和兴起归功于6部电影，除本片外，另外5部分别是《[[活死人之夜|活死人之夜]]》、《[[鼹鼠_(电影)|鼹鼠]]》（{{lang|es|''El Topo}}''）、《[[粉红色的火烈鸟|粉红色的火烈鸟]]》、《[[不速之客_(电影)|不速之客]]》（{{lang|en|''The Harder They Come''}}）和《[[洛基恐怖秀|洛基恐怖秀]]》（{{lang|en|''The Rocky Horror Picture Show''}}）<ref name="margin">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208062902/http://www.allrovi.com/movies/movie/midnight-movies-from-the-margin-to-the-mainstream-v327348 |title=Midnight Movies: From the Margin to the Mainstream – Cast, Reviews, Summary, and Awards |work=Allmovie |publisher=AllRovi |first=Nathan |last=Southern |accessdate=2011-12-08 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.allrovi.com/movies/movie/midnight-movies-from-the-margin-to-the-mainstream-v327348 |archivedate=2011-12-08 }}</ref>。2010年，[[在线影评人协会|在线影评人协会]]编制了一份名单，列出100部最优秀的导演处女作。《橡皮头》在其中名列第二，仅次于[[奥逊·威尔斯|奥逊·威尔斯]]1941年的《[[公民凯恩|公民凯恩]]》<ref name="online100">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-05-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504072722/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/online-critics-post-top-100-directorial-debuts-of-alltime-2099107.html?origin=internalSearch | work = The Independent | deadurl = no | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/online-critics-post-top-100-directorial-debuts-of-alltime-2099107.html?origin=internalSearch | title = Online critics post top 100 directorial debuts of all-time | publisher = Independent Print Limited | date = 2010-10-06 | accessdate = 2014-09-05}}</ref>。

林奇还会在之后的电影中与《橡皮头》的大部分演员和剧组人员合作。弗雷德里克·埃姆斯之后将担任《蓝丝绒》<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|53}}、[[1988年电影|1988年]]的短片《牛仔与法国人》（{{lang|en|''The Cowboy and the Frenchman''}}），以及《我心狂野》的摄影师<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|62-63}}。阿兰·斯普里特将担任《象人》、《沙丘》和《蓝丝绒》的音效设计师<ref name="splet rovi">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131106010852/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0819263/#sound_department | deadurl = no | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0819263/#sound_department | title = Alan Splet (1939–1994) | work = IMDb.com | publisher = amazon.com | accessdate = 2014-09-05}}</ref>。杰克·菲斯克曾担任过林奇1992年的电视剧集《直播》（{{lang|en|''On the Air''}}）中几集节目的导演<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|87}}，还曾在1999年的《[[史崔特先生的故事|史崔特先生的故事]]》（{{lang|en|''The Straight Story''}}）和2001年的《[[穆赫兰大道_(电影)|穆赫兰大道]]》中担任艺术指导设计师<ref name="fisk rovi">{{cite web | url = https://ca.movies.yahoo.com/person/jack-fisk/biography.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140905130628/https://ca.movies.yahoo.com/person/jack-fisk/biography.html | title = Jack Fisk- Biography | work = Yahoo! Movies | publisher = Yahoo | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-09-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。库尔森和南斯都曾参加《双峰》<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|69}}、《沙丘》<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|46}}、《蓝丝绒》<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|53}}、《我心狂野》<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|63}}以及1997年电影《[[妖夜慌踪|妖夜慌踪]]》（{{lang|en|''Lost Highway''}}）的演出<ref name="Odell-Le Blanc-2007" />{{rp|95}}。

《橡皮头》上映后，林奇试图为自己下一个项目《[[火箭罗尼|火箭罗尼]]》（{{lang|en|''Ronnie Rocket''}}）寻求资金，该片讲述“有关电力和一个红头发并且长着三条腿的家伙”的故事<ref name="Rodley-Lynch-2005" />{{rp|91}}。林奇在此期间见到了电影制片人斯图尔特·康菲尔德（{{lang|en|Stuart Cornfeld}}），后者很喜欢《橡皮头》，并且也有兴趣制作《火箭罗尼》。康菲尔德当时为[[梅尔·布鲁克斯|梅尔·布鲁克斯]]和布鲁克斯影业工作，之后林奇和康菲尔德都意识到《火箭罗尼》不大可能筹集到拍摄所需资金，于是林奇请康菲尔德找一些已经写好的剧本，自己想挑选一个来作为下一个项目，康菲尔德找了4个感觉林奇会有兴趣的剧本，最后导演选择的是《象人》<ref name="Rodley-Lynch-2005" />{{rp|92}}。

制作《象人》期间，林奇见到了导演[[斯坦利·库布里克|斯坦利·库布里克]]，库布里克向他透露，《橡皮头》是自己最喜欢的电影<ref name="Lynch-2006">{{cite book | title = Catching the Big Fish: Meditation, Consciousness, and Creativity | url = https://archive.org/details/catchingbigfishm00lync | first = David | last = Lynch | publisher = Jeremy P. Tarcher Inc. | year = 2006 | isbn = 978-0-641-91061-6 | page = [https://archive.org/details/catchingbigfishm00lync/page/89 89]}}</ref>，该片还对库布里克1980年的作品《[[闪灵_(电影)|闪灵]]》产生了影响，据报道称，他曾向该片的演员和剧组成员放映《橡皮头》，让他们了解自己希望《闪灵》表现出的意境<ref>{{cite web | title = Eraserhead, The Short Films Of David Lynch | last = Roberts | url = http://www.uncut.co.uk/david-lynch/eraserhead-the-short-films-of-david-lynch-review | first = Chris | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212011426/http://www.uncut.co.uk/david-lynch/eraserhead-the-short-films-of-david-lynch-review | work = uncut.co.uk | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《橡皮头》还对日本电影人[[冢本晋也|冢本晋也]]1989年的惊悚片《[[铁男1：金属兽|铁男1：金属兽]]》（{{lang|ja|鉄男：Tetsuo}}）、1990年的实验性恐怖片《[[受生|受生]]》，以及[[戴伦·艾洛诺夫斯基|戴伦·艾洛诺夫斯基]]1998年的导演处女作《[[死亡密码|死亡密码]]》（π）构成了影响<ref name="Harper-2007">{{cite book | title = The Unsilvered Screen: Surrealism on film | first = Graeme | last = Harper | year = 2007 | publisher = Wallflower Press | isbn = 978-1-904764-86-1 | edition = illustrated | page = 140}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | url = http://www.film.com/movies/whats-the-big-deal-eraserhead-1977 | title = What's the big deal?: Eraserhead (1977) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103063047/http://www.film.com/movies/whats-the-big-deal-eraserhead-1977 | deadurl = yes | last = Snider | first = Eric D | work = film.com | accessdate = 2014-09-05 }}</ref><ref>Vaughan, Robin. "''Pi'' movie adds up to stimulating analysis." ''The Boston Herald''. Herald Media Inc. October Ironh4, 2004.</ref>。[[瑞士|瑞士]]超现实主义艺术家[[H·R·吉格尔|H·R·吉格尔]]称《橡皮头》是他“所看过最伟大的电影之一”<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103061926/http://www.littlegiger.com/articles/files/Cinefantastique_09_01.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.littlegiger.com/articles/files/Cinefantastique_09_01.pdf | title = H. R. Giger - Alien Design | work = littlegiger.com | publisher = ''Cinefantastique'' | last = Levy | first = Frederic Albert | accessdate = 2014-09-05}}</ref>，还称该片比他自己的作品更接近他的设想<ref>{{cite book | last = Giger | first = Hans Ruedi | others = Translated by Karen Williams | title = HR Giger Arh+ | publisher = Taschen | year = 1993 | isbn = 978-3-8228-9642-6}}</ref>。据吉格尔称，林奇曾拒绝在《沙丘》中与他合作，因为这位导演觉得吉格尔“窃取了他的理念”<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140702172824/http://www.vice.com/read/hr-giger-works-weekends | archivedate = 2014-07-02 | url = http://www.vice.com/read/hr-giger-works-weekends | title = HR GIGER WORKS WEEKENDS | author = Alex | work = vice.com | accessdate = 2014-09-05}}</ref>。

